=============================
JPAContainer AddressBook Demo
=============================

--------
Tutorial
--------

The JPAContainer AddressBook Demo is documented in the JPAContainer Tutorial
included in the JPAContainer installation package as well as at
http://vaadin.com/download/jpacontainer-tutorial/ .

---------------------
Compiling and Running
---------------------

You should be able to compile the demo as a deployable WAR package with
the "package" phase.

You can also run it in the Jetty web server in port 8080 with the jetty:run
goal as follows:

$ mvn jetty:run 

--------------------
Importing to Eclipse
--------------------

You should be able to import the demo project in Eclipse as a Maven project.
You will need the m2e plugin for Eclipse. Please see the Tutorial
for more detailed instructions.
